text:
Given the disproportionate impact of #covid19 on BAME communities, I asked at health committee, what proportion of contact tracers are BAME?

Baroness Harding did not know the answer.

Testing & tracing needs to work for everyone, especially those most vulnerable to the virus. https://t.co/Fs0LYyvaiY
